    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Note that you have some JS issues here... `await array.forEach(...)` won't do anything, because `array.forEach()` returns `undefined` - so you're kicking off a bunch of promises but not awaiting those promises.\r\n\r\nThe right way to do this would be something like:\r\n```javascript\r\nawait Promise.all(\r\n  array.map(async (item) => { /* ... */ })\r\n);\r\n```",
